file.name: openapi2.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Entities
  version: "1.0"
paths:
  /:
    get:
      tags:
        - person
      operationId: getRoot
      responses:
        "200":
          description: ""
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Person"
components:
  schemas:
    Person:
      required:
        - name
        - age
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        age:
          type: integer
